{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1681-04_37","head":{"value":"Fable","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", avril 1681 [tome 4], p. 37-40.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"En attendant la Réponse que je veux croire qu’on fera à cette Lettre, je vous envoye une Fable, dont les Médisans tireront beaucoup de fruit, s’ils en examinent la moralité. Elle est de l’Anonime d’Alais, qui leur découvre les maux que produit leur langue, en leur apprenant que la réputation perduë ne sçauroit se recouvrer.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"FABLE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Feu, la Renommée, &amp; l’Onde,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Resolurent un jour d’aller courir le Monde.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne sçay point quel estoit le sujet","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un semblable projet,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si c’estoit l’interest, le caprice, ou la gloire,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’on n’en dit rien dans leur Histoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je n’en parleray point aussi.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seulement veux-je dire icy","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que l’Onde avec le Feu, quoy que si fort contraires,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chercherent de concert les moyens necessaires","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour se retrouver aisément,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En cas de quelque égarement ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et mesme, qui plus est, contre toute apparence","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dés la premiere conférence,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils tomberent d’accord que chacun à son tour","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Donneroit un signal pour marquer son sejour.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Eau donna donc le sien, &amp; dit,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/hi/#"}},"#":{"value":" Si je m’égare,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/#"}},"Ou qu’un autre accident en chemin nous sépare,","Vous n’aurez qu’à vous rendre où vous verrez des Joncs,","J’y seray sans faillir, ou bien aux environs.",{"#1":{"value":"Quant au mien, ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[20]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"dit le Feu,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[20]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" ce sera la Fumée.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[20]/#2"}},{"#":{"value":" Pour moy, ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[21]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"leur dit la Renommée,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[21]/hi/#"}}}," Je ne donneray pas le mien,","Mais songez à me tenir bien,","Car déslors qu’une fois j’échape,"," Jamais plus on ne me ratrape."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toy qui te plais à déchirer,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dont la médisance est par tout répanduë,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tremble d’un mal qu’en vain tu voudras reparer ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La réputation perduë","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne peut jamais se recouvrer.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}